昂.definition: to lift; to raise; to raise one's head; high; high spirits; soaring; expensive

昂山素姬.definition: see 昂山素季[Ang2 Shan1 Su4 Ji4]

昂藏.definition: tall and strongly built; stalwart; courageous

昂首.definition: head high; in high spirits; to raise one's head (e.g. of neighing horse)
